<html lang="ko"> <!-- ko로 바꾸는 이유 : ko 로 안하면 번역 옵션이 뜸, 한글 페이지란 뜻임 -->
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- defer reference : ex15 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home/login.css">
    <script src="/js/home/login.js" defer></script>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-page">
        <div class="form">
          <form class="login-form">
            <input id="id" type="text" placeholder="아이디"/>
            <input id="name" type="text" placeholder="이름"/>
            <input id="pwd" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호"/>
            <input id="confirm-pwd" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호 확인"/>
            <button>SIGN UP</button>
            <p class="message">Already registered? <a href="/login">login</a></p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
</body>
</html>

